Within the Industrial Division, Business Unit CO2 markets liquid carbon dioxide and dry-ice in Western Europe and Scandinavia. The production assets are located in a number of countries and liquid carbon dioxide is supplied across borders by road tanker and ship. This response is only relevant for Business Unit CO2, not Yara Industrial or Yara International.'
